data.description: A must see beautiful 2-story home with inground heated pool in Round Lake Estates. The privacy fence and flower gardens complete the outdoor oasis with the cedar deck and paved patio. All newer stainless steel appliances and much of the HVAC has been updated as well. It also has a finished basement with living area, bar, and fireplace for entertaining. Spacious owner’s bedroom complete with bayed window sitting area. Conveniently located near Eden Prairie High School and many community parks nearby. Access to Hwy 5, Hwy 62, Hwy 212 and 494 nearby as well. A one year HSA warranty will also come with the home.
